net.ontopia.topicmaps.utils
Class PSI

java.lang.Object
  net.ontopia.topicmaps.utils.PSI

public class PSI
extends Object

INTERNAL: This class collects core PSIs in a single place as a convenience for topic map developers. See the XTM 1.0 specification for definitions of the meanings of these PSIs.
